---
import CommonHead from "../components/CommonHead.astro";
import GameMechanics from "../components/GameMechanics.astro";
import Poker101 from "../components/Poker101.astro";
import PokerHands from "../components/PokerHands.astro";
import "../styles/global.css";
---

<html lang="en" data-theme="light">
  <head>
    <CommonHead title="Private Poker Night - Rules & Etiquette" description="Learn the rules and etiquette for our private poker night event" />
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/daisyui@5" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tailwindcss/browser@4"></script>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@700&family=Lato:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
      .card-example {
        font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;
        font-size: 1.25rem;
        font-weight: bold;
      }
      .red-suit {
        color: #CC0000;
      }
      .black-suit {
        color: #000000;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body class="font-[Lato] bg-base-100 text-base-content min-h-screen">
    <div class="container mx-auto p-4 md:p-8 max-w-5xl">
      <header class="text-center my-8">
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold">Private Poker Night</h1>
        <p class="text-lg mt-2">An Exclusive Evening of Cards & Camaraderie</p>
      </header>

      <div role="tablist" class="tabs tabs-lifted mb-8">
        <input type="radio" name="poker_tabs" role="tab" class="tab" aria-label="The Invitation" checked />
        <div role="tabpanel" class="tab-content bg-base-100 border-base-300 rounded-box p-6">
          <div class="bg-white/70 p-6 md:p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg border border-gray-100">
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4 text-gray-800">Welcome to the Table</h2>
            <p class="mb-6 text-gray-700 text-base md:text-lg">This section provides all the essential details for our exclusive event. We aim to create a fun, safe, and respectful environment for a friendly game of strip poker among a small group of participants.</p>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
              <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg border border-gray-100 shadow-sm">
                <h3 class="font-bold text-xl mb-2 text-gray-800">Event Details</h3>
                <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-600 text-base">
                  <li class="flex items-center"><span class="mr-3 text-xl text-yellow-600">●</span><strong>Seating:</strong> Limited to 5 participants</li>
                  <li class="flex items-center"><span class="mr-3 text-xl text-yellow-600">●</span><strong>Entry Fee:</strong> $25 (for event entry, not gambling)</li>
                  <li class="flex items-center"><span class="mr-3 text-xl text-yellow-600">●</span><strong>Refreshments:</strong> BYOB, sharing is encouraged</li>
                  <li class="flex items-center"><span class="mr-3 text-xl text-yellow-600">●</span><strong>Duration:</strong> 8:00 PM - 11:00 PM (First hand at 8:30 PM)</li>
                </ul>
                <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700 font-semibold text-base">The exact address will be provided upon payment of the entry fee. Your payment signifies acceptance and consent to all the rules of the game and the host's establishment, as detailed on this page.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg border border-gray-100 shadow-sm">
                <h3 class="font-bold text-xl mb-2 text-gray-800">About Our Game Night</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-base">This event centers around a beginner-friendly game of strip poker, designed for fun and strategic play in a safe, consensual space. Please remember, this is strictly a card game for entertainment and is <strong class="text-red-700">not a sex party</strong>.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <input type="radio" name="poker_tabs" role="tab" class="tab" aria-label="House Rules" />
        <div role="tabpanel" class="tab-content bg-base-100 border-base-300 rounded-box p-6">
                <div class="bg-amber-50 p-6 md:p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-amber-200">
                    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-amber-800">Event Rules & Consensual Game Etiquette</h2>
                    <p class="mb-6 text-amber-700">This is the most important section. To ensure a fun and comfortable experience for everyone, please review the following essential rules on safety and consent. Adherence is non-negotiable.</p>
                    <div class="space-y-4">
                        <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-center text-amber-900 p-4 bg-amber-100 rounded-md">Consent is mandatory for everything.</p>
                        <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
                            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="mr-3 mt-1 text-lg text-amber-600">✔</span><span><strong>No Unwanted Contact:</strong> Includes all forms of physical touch, suggestive body gestures, and inappropriate or unwanted speech.</span></li>
                            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="mr-3 mt-1 text-lg text-amber-600">✔</span><span><strong>Host's Authority:</strong> The host ("The Princess") rules the Palace. If the host feels uncomfortable for any reason, you will be asked to leave.</span></li>
                            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="mr-3 mt-1 text-lg text-amber-600">✔</span><span><strong>Ongoing Consent:</strong> A visible item will signify ongoing consent. If anyone feels uncomfortable, the game will pause until consent from all players is re-established.</span></li>
                            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="mr-3 mt-1 text-lg text-amber-600">✔</span><span><strong>Behavior Policy:</strong> You will receive **one warning** for out-of-line behavior. A second instance means you will be asked to leave.</span></li>
                            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="mr-3 mt-1 text-lg text-amber-600">✔</span><span><strong>Collective Safety:</strong> If someone is asked to leave, you are expected to side with the host. We collectively create a safe space.</span></li>
                            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="mr-3 mt-1 text-lg text-amber-600">✔</span><span><strong>Nudity Is Not an Invitation:</strong> Nudity is a consequence of the game, not an invitation for contact. Players may redress at the end of a round.</span></li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
        </div>

        <input type="radio" name="poker_tabs" role="tab" class="tab" aria-label="Game Mechanics" />
        <div role="tabpanel" class="tab-content bg-base-100 border-base-300 rounded-box p-6">
			<GameMechanics />
        </div>

        <input type="radio" name="poker_tabs" role="tab" class="tab" aria-label="Poker 101" />
        <div role="tabpanel" class="tab-content bg-base-100 border-base-300 rounded-box p-6">
			<Poker101 />
        </div>

        <input type="radio" name="poker_tabs" role="tab" class="tab" aria-label="Poker Hands" />
        <div role="tabpanel" class="tab-content bg-base-100 border-base-300 rounded-box p-6">
            <PokerHands />
        </div>

        <input type="radio" name="poker_tabs" role="tab" class="tab" aria-label="Variations" />
        <div role="tabpanel" class="tab-content bg-base-100 border-base-300 rounded-box p-6">
                <div class="bg-white/50 p-6 md:p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
                    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Optional Game Variations</h2>
                    <p class="mb-6 text-gray-700">To keep things interesting, the host ("The Princess") may introduce one of the following variations after the first game, at her discretion.</p>
                    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg border border-gray-100">
                            <h3 class="font-bold text-xl mb-2">1. Progressive Ante</h3>
                            <p class="text-gray-600">The ante increases by 1 point each round (e.g., 1 point in round 1, 2 points in round 2, etc.).</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg border border-gray-100">
                            <h3 class="font-bold text-xl mb-2">2. House Collects Pot</h3>
                            <p class="text-gray-600">The house collects the entire pot. The winner of the hand receives their initial bid back (not the ante).</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg border border-gray-100">
                            <h3 class="font-bold text-xl mb-2">3. No Chips/Points</h3>
                            <p class="text-gray-600">The player who loses a round directly loses a clothing article according to the removal order.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg border border-gray-100">
                            <h3 class="font-bold text-xl mb-2">4. Princess's Advantage</h3>
                            <p class="text-gray-600">The host acts as the dealer with extra face-up cards, increasing her odds. If she wins, she chooses who removes an article of clothing.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
          </main>

    <!-- Theme Toggle -->
    <div class="fixed bottom-4 right-4">
      <label class="swap swap-flip text-4xl">
        <input type="checkbox" class="theme-controller" value="dark" />
        <svg class="swap-on fill-current w-10 h-10" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path d="M5.64,17l-.71.71a1,1,0,0,0,0,1.41,1,1,0,0,0,1.41,0l.71-.71A1,1,0,0,0,5.64,17ZM5,12a1,1,0,0,0-1-1H3a1,1,0,0,0,0,2H4A1,1,0,0,0,5,12Zm7-7a1,1,0,0,0,1-1V3a1,1,0,0,0-2,0V4A1,1,0,0,0,12,5ZM5.64,7.05a1,1,0,0,0,.7.29,1,1,0,0,0,.71-.29,1,1,0,0,0,0-1.41l-.71-.71A1,1,0,0,0,4.93,6.34Zm12,.29a1,1,0,0,0,.7-.29l.71-.71a1,1,0,1,0-1.41-1.41L17,5.64a1,1,0,0,0,0,1.41A1,1,0,0,0,17.66,7.34ZM21,11H20a1,1,0,0,0,0,2h1a1,1,0,0,0,0-2Zm-9,8a1,1,0,0,0-1,1v1a1,1,0,0,0,2,0V20A1,1,0,0,0,12,19ZM18.36,16.83a1,1,0,0,0-1.41,1.41l.71.71a1,1,0,0,0,1.41,0,1,1,0,0,0,0-1.41ZM12,6.5A5.5,5.5,0,1,0,17.5,12,5.51,5.51,0,0,0,12,6.5Zm0,9A3.5,3.5,0,1,1,15.5,12,3.5,3.5,0,0,1,12,15.5Z"/>
        </svg>
        <svg class="swap-off fill-current w-10 h-10" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path d="M21.64,13a1,1,0,0,0-1.05-.14,8.05,8.05,0,0,1-3.37.73A8.15,8.15,0,0,1,9.08,5.49a8.59,8.59,0,0,1,.25-2A1,1,0,0,0,8,2.36,10.14,10.14,0,1,0,22,14.05,1,1,0,0,0,21.64,13Zm-9.5,6.69A8.14,8.14,0,0,1,7.08,5.22v.27A10.15,10.15,0,0,0,17.22,15.63a9.79,9.79,0,0,0,2.1-.22A8.11,8.11,0,0,1,12.14,19.73Z"/>
        </svg>
      </label>
    </div>

  </body>
</html>
